  "body": "The following cases should be considered in the design:\r\n- a depiction of how a card will appear if the whole community requires three different tokens to unlock\r\n- a depiction of how a card will appear if a whole community requires two different tokens to unlock OR requires a different set of 3 tokens to unlock\r\n- the overflow pattern that should be displayed if a community requires many different combinations of tokens to unlock\r\n\r\nHere the figma:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Mobile-Components?node-id=911%3A27048\r\n\r\nAlso it is needed to add a tooltip when hovering the requirements row area like it is suggested here (and agreed with the designers): https://github.com/status-im/StatusQ/pull/712#issuecomment-1149648653\r\n\r\nAnd also it is needed to clarify radius discussion https://github.com/status-im/StatusQ/pull/712#discussion_r889985576  with designers.",
